<section id="ch12">
  <div class="chapter-header" data-ch="12">
    <div class="ch-label">Chapter 12</div>
    <h2>Defense Mechanisms &amp; Writing Winning Reports</h2>
    <p>Understanding defenses makes you a better attacker. Writing great reports gets you paid.</p>
