2. Navigate to [exact path to feature]
3. Intercept with Burp Suite
4. Modify the request:
   [Exact HTTP request with highlighted change]
5. Observe the response contains:
   [Exact relevant portion of AWS metadata response]

<span class="ok">## Impact</span>
An unauthenticated/authenticated attacker can:
- Retrieve temporary AWS credentials for IAM role: [ROLE-NAME]
- The attached policy [POLICY-NAME] grants: [list permissions]
