2. Block requests to RFC1918, loopback, and link-local ranges
3. Enforce AWS IMDSv2 (require PUT token for all metadata requests)
4. Apply least-privilege to the IAM role attached to this instance
5. Consider disabling metadata service access entirely if not required</pre>

